{
  "3152710": {
    "name": "House Of Horror: Outside Is Better",
    "steam_appid": 3152710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/070f5e086f702fae9fa0051817550675.poster.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/070f5e086f702fae9fa0051817550675.webm?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/070f5e086f702fae9fa0051817550675.mp4?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《HOUSE OF HORROR: OUTSIDE IS BETTER》</strong> 是一款第一人称心理生存恐怖游戏，将玩家带入一场令人不寒而栗的恐怖冒险，旨在将紧张感、悬疑感与心理承受能力推向极限，甚至挑战该类型中最经验丰富的玩家。准备探索一座噩梦般的酷刑设施，这里被表现出极端暴力行为的精神病患者所占据。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/9578c3e25e7f02ba96f5cd8c6ae46957.poster.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/9578c3e25e7f02ba96f5cd8c6ae46957.webm?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/9578c3e25e7f02ba96f5cd8c6ae46957.mp4?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场沉浸式的恐怖体验，将悬疑、恐惧与心理压迫完美融合，在一个几乎无法逃脱的地方考验玩家的生存极限。由恐怖类型资深开发者打造，即使是最老练的玩家也将面临严峻挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/3740eb47e565aeedf82df7686eccdb8f.webp?t=1767719613\" width=74 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/e71d3f6855752fd840ec595d3b8f7af2.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设定在一座被改造成真正噩梦的精神病酷刑设施中，将玩家彻底带入一个黑暗、压迫且令人极度不安的环境。通过精心设计的氛围恐怖与声音驱动的惊悚效果，每一条走廊、每一个房间、每一道阴影都成为持续存在的威胁。游戏中的每一分钟都旨在不断放大恐惧，并将紧张感维持在最高点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/7cf96f0c990bf6f41afde5bac33dd635.poster.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/7cf96f0c990bf6f41afde5bac33dd635.webm?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/7cf96f0c990bf6f41afde5bac33dd635.mp4?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作融合了 FPS 玩法、密室逃脱式挑战与环境叙事，呈现出这一既残酷又迷人的类型所应具备的一切。玩家必须解开谜题、合理管理稀缺资源，并在与极度暴力的精神病患者的遭遇中存活下来——在这个几乎无法逃脱的地方，前进是唯一的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事通过章节式的冒险逐步展开，每一章都由与这座恐怖设施相关的不同角色担任主角。每个章节都提供独特的视角，引入新的玩法机制，并揭示关键的叙事碎片，最终共同拼凑出隐藏在这座机构背后的黑暗真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一座秘密的地下设施深处，精神病患者被逼至疯狂边缘，无法控制的暴力行为释放出难以言喻的恐怖。这座曾经用于人体实验与残酷折磨的扭曲监狱，如今已成为你的生存竞技场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在毫无记忆的情况下醒来，被迫拼凑这里曾发生的骇人实验与非人道试验。随着不断深入，你逐渐发现隐藏在疯狂背后的邪恶力量——一种能够扭曲现实本身的存在。要想在这场可怕的经历中生存下来，不仅需要智慧，更需要保持理智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由拥有大型娱乐制作经验的恐怖类型资深开发者打造，《House of Horror: Outside Is Better》带来了一场扎实、沉浸且精心设计的生存恐怖体验，旨在扰乱心智、挑战极限并带来真正的恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/e3102952eacdd42bd360abffac020aa7.webp?t=1767719613\" width=121 height=22 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在设施内部，你将使用一块<strong>目标腕表</strong>作为主要的导航与指引工具。该设备不仅用于引导你的任务目标与进度，同时还充当一种<strong>积分/信用系统</strong>，使你能够获取不同资源、解锁奖励，并做出直接影响生存的战略性决策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/c4b630771b8a4f31e63b1f5f3f069e61.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了在这段体验中存活下来，你必须依赖一把<strong>手摇发电手电筒</strong>——这一关键道具强化了沉浸感与持续不断的紧张氛围。它的使用需要精细的管理，迫使你在照亮黑暗与盲目前行之间做出抉择，从而进一步加深心理恐怖的压迫感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/5d7700fc4732f65a4f94ed20a5a1f65c.poster.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/5d7700fc4732f65a4f94ed20a5a1f65c.webm?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/5d7700fc4732f65a4f94ed20a5a1f65c.mp4?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗采用生存恐怖风格的 FPS 机制，玩家只能使用有限的武器库，包括左轮手枪、霰弹枪、手枪及其他工具。由于弹药极其稀缺，每一次遭遇都必须谨慎评估，每一个决定都可能成为生与死的分水岭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/9eb9512a0594f120041bddfc82143b97.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作采用沉浸式第一人称模拟体验，融合步行模拟要素、叙事探索以及结合 3D 音效的氛围恐怖，打造出一种强烈压迫感的感官体验。在这里，环境、本身的声音以及与世界持续不断的互动，同样危险，甚至不亚于潜伏其中的敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/0473cb8fffce9695b33a4e157377fd3f.poster.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/0473cb8fffce9695b33a4e157377fd3f.webm?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/0473cb8fffce9695b33a4e157377fd3f.mp4?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/afce5a2180638bd4f90c0745679ee374.webp?t=1767719613\" width=111 height=23 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真正的生存恐怖：</strong><br>在某些时刻，你将毫无防御——没有武器，也没有盟友，只能选择逃跑、躲藏，并以智慧战胜你那些扭曲的追捕者。而在其他时刻，你则需要面对紧张而直接的动态对抗。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理恐怖：</strong><br>体验一段令人不安的故事，随着每一次真相的揭露，理智逐渐被侵蚀，恐惧与精神崩溃相互交织。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式视觉表现：</strong><br>高质量的画面将玩家带入一个黑暗而封闭的环境，每迈出一步，紧张感都在不断攀升。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不可预测的敌人：</strong><br>精神病患者的行为毫无规律——他们可能悄无声息地尾随你，也可能在任何时刻突然爆发出暴力攻击。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗主题：</strong><br>心理虐待、酷刑与疯狂等主题贯穿始终，营造出一种深度不安、令人压迫的整体氛围。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/a70d6f34611be1df525a6dd9a9b7053c.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/67253a7b283a253df54936559fe22640.webp?t=1767719613\" width=110 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/76fe6c734d9644946ceb4a6dbf8a8d48.poster.avif?t=1767719613\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/76fe6c734d9644946ceb4a6dbf8a8d48.webm?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152710/extras/76fe6c734d9644946ceb4a6dbf8a8d48.mp4?t=1767719613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《HOUSE OF HORROR: OUTSIDE IS BETTER》</strong> 包含血腥暴力、令人不安的画面、裸露内容以及强烈的心理主题。强烈建议玩家谨慎体验。本游戏还包含可能引发光敏反应的场景。任何与现实事件或人物的相似之处均属纯属巧合。</p>",
